first_reading.text:
[[Is 48,17]]Thus says the LORD, your redeemer, the Holy One of Israel: I, the LORD, your God, teach you what is for your good, and lead you on the way you should go.
[[Is 48,18]]If you would hearken to my commandments, your prosperity would be like a river, and your vindication like the waves of the sea;
[[Is 48,19]]Your descendants would be like the sand, and those born of your stock like its grains, Their name never cut off or blotted out from my presence.
